Package: indicate
Title: INDICATE Minimal Data Dictionary Explorer
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Boris", "Delange", , "boris.delange@univ-rennes.fr", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: An interactive Shiny application to explore the INDICATE Minimal
    Data Dictionary, a consensus-based collection of standardized clinical
    concepts for harmonizing intensive care unit (ICU) data across Europe. The
    application provides tools to explore standardized terminologies (SNOMED CT,
    LOINC, RxNorm, ICD-10), perform semantic alignment, and propose improvements
    to the dictionary.
